div.p:
3. Level of Response. Matmon C can be broken down into
                    several categories for analytical purposes: follow-on support requirements;
                    items for modernization of forces; high technology to enhance force efficiency;
                    and force expansion. There was general agreement that we should be prepared to
                    make positive decisions concerning follow-on support and should consider
                    requests in the other categories on a case-by-case basis.
